Legendary Entertainment Will Raise $220.5 Million for Hong Kong Venture

-- B y   A n t h o n y   P a l a z z o
-- 
2011-08-21T14:48:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-21/legendary-entertainment-will-raise-220-5-million-for-hong-kong-venture.html
Legendary Entertainment, the film
production company behind “Inception” and the “Hangover”
movies, will raise $220.5 million for a  Hong Kong  venture
through Paul Y. Engineering Group Ltd.  Paul Y. Engineering will fund its 50 percent stake by
selling new shares to private equity firm AID Partners and,
through UBS AG, selling shares to other investors, the Hong
Kong-based company said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anthony Palazzo in Los Angeles at 
 apalazzo@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
